Sentencas: Proton-conductive SrZrO3 films were successfully deposited on Pt/SiOx/Si and porous stainless-steel substrates by liquid delivery metal-organic chemical vapor deposition (LD-MOCVD).
Titulo: Deposition of SrZrO3 Thin Films Using Liquid Delivery Metal-Organic Chemical Vapor Deposition

Sentencas: The as-deposited films deposited on the Pt/SiOx/Si substrate at 600 degrees C showed good crystallinity and post-annealing at temperatures below 800 degrees C resulted in improved crystallinity.
Titulo: Deposition of SrZrO3 Thin Films Using Liquid Delivery Metal-Organic Chemical Vapor Deposition

Sentencas: A 200-nm-thick film deposited on the porous stainless-steel substrate was flat and solid and did not show any gas leakage.
Titulo: Deposition of SrZrO3 Thin Films Using Liquid Delivery Metal-Organic Chemical Vapor Deposition

Sentencas: We consider this deposition technique to be applicable for the fabrication of a new solid oxide fuel cell structure with intermediate-temperature operation.
Titulo: Deposition of SrZrO3 Thin Films Using Liquid Delivery Metal-Organic Chemical Vapor Deposition
